\pard\pardeftab720\sa240

\b0\fs24 \cf0 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
The DIRAC Institute: The Data Intensive Research in Astrophysics and Cosmology Institute is a world leading, interdisciplinary research center that addresses fundamental questions about the origins and evolution of our universe. \
Our research brings together scientists across many disciplines on a mission to understand the nature of Dark Matter and Dark Energy, the emergence of structure within the universe, the formation of galaxies, the birth and evolution of black holes, the transformations of stars, and the origins of the planets. \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
