8.4 meter, wide-field, f/1.2 telescope.\uc0\u8232 3.2 Gigapixel, 189 4k x 4k CCD camera, with 2-second readout.\u8232 PetaFLOPS of computing power, hundreds of PB of storage, gigabit long-haul networks.\
